>\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"cba04bdd7f8b31bc4470e8ff133deab18495e12d","tid":2068670,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T01:33:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\">一日到黑就淨係錢, 樓價股價, 69已經話緊人收錢出黎行</span><br />\n會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#20241 - 打邊爐家族-爸爸</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請保持批判性思考，善用「上一頁」和「不推文回覆」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">該會員以往言論 (13)：</div><code>1 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/eHiuaT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/eHiuaT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">藍屍言論</span><br />\n<code>2 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/eBmMHT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/eBmMHT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠</span><br />\n<code>3 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/eoCODT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/eoCODT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">藍屍言論 支持警察射死暴徒</span><br />\n<code>4 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/eiGoxT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/eiGoxT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">藍屍言論</span><br />\n<code>5 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/ehrMeT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/ehrMeT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">藍屍言論</span><br />\n<code>6 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/dzEjrT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/dzEjrT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">藍屍言論 請中央救香港人</span><br />\n<code>7 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/dpMOkT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/dpMOkT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">藍屍言論</span><br />\n<code>8 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/dapbzT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/dapbzT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">藍屍言論</span><br />\n<code>9 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/cQBqKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/cQBqKT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">藍屍言論</span><br />\n<code>10.</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/cOixiT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/cOixiT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">藍屍言論</span><br />\n<code>11.</code><a hr